      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Gareth Davies has been Director General, Business and Science since 2015.</p>

<p>Before joining the department he worked for AIA in south east Asia leading on finance and operational transformation. Over the last decade Gareth has worked in Downing Street as the Prime Minister’s lead adviser on welfare reform, been Head of the Prime Minister’s Strategy Unit and was an Executive Board member of both the Cabinet Office and the Department for Innovation Universities and Skills.</p>

<p>Gareth spent his early career in PricewaterhouseCoopers, specialising in privatisation, investment appraisal and competition policy.</p>

</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_3818">
            <h1 id="director-general-business-and-science">Director General, Business and Science</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General is responsible for the following areas:</p>

<ul>
  <li>industrial strategy</li>
  <li>advanced manufacturing</li>
  <li>infrastructure and materials</li>
  <li>life sciences</li>
  <li>professional and business services</li>
  <li>retail</li>
  <li>science, research and innovation</li>
  <li>small business and entrepreneurs</li>
  <li>UK Research & Innovation</li>
  <li>UK Space Agency</li>
  <li>Intellectual Property Office</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
